{"tid":2219982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣布，陳同佳都係受害者","createTime":"2020-09-27T09:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T05:51:08.000Z","uid":116960,"like":14,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"11161641970332f7de5e0e48574ce8b8cd33328c","tid":2219982,"uid":116960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:36:42.000Z","msg":"戴完綠帽，比條女呃去台灣諗住比佢中出然後埋單幫手養仔。之後仲要比林病擺上檯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗深一層冇陳同佳，林病點都係搵過第二個籍口。<br />\n仲要條女藍絲老豆老母第一時間搵保皇黨幫手，拒絕黃媒訪問。搞左成年而家見報唔到仇啦就係咁接受黃媒訪問諗住比群眾壓力佢。<br />\n講真送中單野真係唔怪得佳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢只不過係個比mk妹戴綠帽的可憐蟲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eca1b1d00ec1327b951f4b93a767cecb841c9e9","tid":2219982,"uid":142313,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"下個"},{"pid":"3577be6ce22491f8e540129926ec83c8cad2ca79","tid":2219982,"uid":116960,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"7eca1b1d00ec1327b951f4b93a767cecb841c9e9","tid":2219982,"uid":142313,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"下個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將送中怪係陳同佳到證明你d政治智慧有幾咁低下"},{"pid":"60acadffd3fa2649c3e2630570e3f95670c70f00","tid":2219982,"uid":142313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3577be6ce22491f8e540129926ec83c8cad2ca79","tid":2219982,"uid":116960,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"7eca1b1d00ec1327b951f4b93a767cecb841c9e9","tid":2219982,"uid":142313,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"下個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T10:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將送中怪係陳同佳到證明你d政治智慧有幾咁低下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T11:51:25.000Z","msg":"唔覺佢關事 所以無係唔係受害者一說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" cl